##     - BACKENDS
##     - LINES
##     - PATCHES
##     - HATCHES
##     - BOXPLOT
##     - FONT
##     - TEXT
##     - LaTeX
##     - AXES
##     - DATES
##     - TICKS
##     - GRIDS
##     - LEGEND
##     - FIGURE
##     - IMAGES
##     - CONTOUR PLOTS
##     - ERRORBAR PLOTS
##     - HISTOGRAM PLOTS
##     - SCATTER PLOTS
##     - AGG RENDERING
##     - PATHS
